@NODE BugReports "bugreports"

ATTENTION ! Please do not send me questions about how the HP48 works or
            using the HP48. Please read the manual you got with your HP,
            and/or the FAQ of the HP48 newsgroups.

If you find a bug or a misfeature in Alcuin, or have an idea how
to make things better, then pelase drop me a note so I'll be able 
to improve Alcuin in the future.
My address con be found @{"here" LINK Schupfer}.

Important for a bug report is the following information:

 · Version of Alcuin (can be found by doing "version Alcuin" from Shell)
 · Used Amiga configuration ( e.g. 68030,..,2MB Chip,., OS 3.0,.,serial.device,)
 · Used graphicsmode of the Workbench (e.q. ECS 4 Bit, .., CyberGraphX 8 Bit, ..)
 · Used HP48 ROM version ( e.g. GX : P  etc.)
 · Information about installed startup programs on the Amiga
 · Information about installed programms on Alcuin
 · Alcuin settings
 · Detailed decription what programm or command produces the bug and how
   it can be reproduced.

But first please look, if it's a @{"known bug" LINK Bugs}.

@ENDNODE

